If no sets are defined or queues are not being monitored, this is a finding.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA></STIG_DATA><STIG_DATA><VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE><ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Open the Exchange Management Shell and enter the following command:

